# Product Recommendation System - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

# =============================================================================
# LLM API Configuration (choose one)
# =============================================================================

# Option 1: GitHub Models (recommended - free tier available)
# Get your token at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here

# Option 2: OpenAI API
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option 3: Azure OpenAI (enterprise)
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com/
# AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=your-deployment-name
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_azure_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# Notes
# =============================================================================
# - The system checks for credentials in this order: GitHub > Azure > OpenAI
# - GitHub Models uses gpt-4o-mini by default
# - Only one API configuration is needed
# - Simple Search and Catalog Info work without any API key (uses local embeddings)
